name: Numb
description:
Numb
'Numb' 
This artwork was created when i was dealing with personal problem. Her expression somehow shows that she's getting used by the constant pain of being throbbed by icy block. I choose the icy cold ice block as a metaphor to show that she's emotionally numb. Her problem or pain seems normal to her because she faced the same things every day. Getting used by it, she feels numb and cold-heartless.
